Class VmPush

All Implemented Interfaces:
TrailElement
public class VmPush
extends Push

This TrailElement extends Push and takes an object as its initialization argument. It indicates that this object has to be popped from the current virtual machine stack. It will also restore some of its states.

Version:
1.0.0, 2010-03-18
Author:
Tim Majchrzak
